data.description: This charming and sunny 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style, making it an ideal place to call home.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by the warm glow of recessed lighting in the living area and the timeless elegance of parquet floors throughout. The eat-in kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, and ample cabinet space. Whether you're cooking a gourmet meal or enjoying a quick bite, this kitchen has everything you need.  Storage is plentiful with two large closets at the entrance, perfect for coats and shoes, as well as a large walk-in closet in the bedroom. Plus, a spacious linen closet adds to the practicality of the space.  Enjoy the great open view with views of downtown Bethesda at night. Additionally, its proximity to the elevator ensures convenience and ease of access.  Enjoy worry-free living with ALL utilities included in the condo fee, allowing you to focus on what matters most. Commuting is a breeze with walkable access to the metro and convenient proximity to major highways like I-495 and Rockville Pike.  Experience the best of urban living with nature at your doorstep, as a beautiful park with trails and nature paths awaits just moments away. Take advantage of the impressive community amenities including a laundry room, pool, an on site gym, and a Sky Lounge on the 17th Floor. Plus, with a Grosvenor Market nearby, everyday conveniences are within easy reach.  With 24-hour security and a concierge desk with a security entrance, peace of mind is guaranteed. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional condo your own.
